achievement.description: Defeat Grand Magistrix Elisande in The Nighthold on Mythic difficulty.

achievement.description: Activate both of Fandral's Flames at once in Firelands without any raid member getting hit by Kneel to the Flame!

achievement.title: Glory of the Firelands Raider
achievement.description: Complete the Firelands raid achievements listed below.

achievement.description: Complete the Suramar storylines listed below.

achievement.title: Step Into The Arena
achievement.description: Win a ranked arena match.

achievement.title: Having a Ball
achievement.description: Collect 50 toys.

achievement.title: I've Got My Eyes On You
achievement.description: Defeat Gul'dan in The Nighthold on Normal difficulty or higher, after defeating 16 Eyes of Gul'dan within 3 seconds.

criteria.description: Defeat 16 Eyes of Gul'dan within 3 seconds.

achievement.title: Glory of the Legion Raider
achievement.description: Complete the Legion raid achievements listed below.

achievement.title: Infinitesimal
achievement.description: Get betrayed by and then defeat an Infinite Whelpling during the Grand Magistrix Elisande encounter, then defeat Grand Magistrix Elisande in The Nighthold, on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Burning Bridges
achievement.description: Defeat Krosus in The Nighthold after quenching 15 Burning Embers on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: A Change In Scenery
achievement.description: Engage and defeat Spellblade Aluriel in the following areas of The Nighthold on Normal difficulty or higher. She must reach her destination within 120 seconds of entering combat and remain there until defeated:

achievement.title: Not For You
achievement.description: Defeat Tichondrius in The Nighthold without taking any damage from Echoes of the Void on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Elementalry!
achievement.description: Defeat Star Augur Etraeus in The Nighthold after having defeated a Well-Traveled Nether Elemental on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Fruit of All Evil
achievement.description: Defeat High Botanist Tel'arn in The Nighthold while all members of the raid are afflicted with Arcane Exposure on Normal Difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Cage Rematch
achievement.description: Defeat Skorpyron in The Nighthold on Normal difficulty or higher without any player leaving the center rings.

criteria.description: All players inside the center rings.

achievement.title: I Attack the Darkness
achievement.description: Defeat a Creature in the Dark during each of phase of the encounter with Xavius in The Emerald Nightmare on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Webbing Crashers
achievement.description: Defeat Elerethe Renferal in The Emerald Nightmare after destroying all her Pulsing Egg Sacs during the encounter on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Took the Red Eye Down
achievement.description: Defeat Il'gynoth in The Emerald Nightmare after inflicting 20 Nightmare Explosions on the Eye of Il'gynoth within 10 seconds on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Imagined Dragons World Tour
achievement.description: Defeat Ysondre in The Emerald Nightmare while all members of the raid have Dream Essences from all four gateway locations on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Buggy Fight
achievement.description: Defeat Nythendra in The Emerald Nightmare after squishing 15 Glow Bugs on Normal difficulty or higher.

achievement.title: Champions Rise
achievement.description: Raise 8 Class Hall Champions to level 110.

Freezing Trap

When Freezing Trap's incapacitate effect ends, the victim and all nearby enemies' movement speed is reduced by 50% for 4 sec.



Explosive Trap

Tar Trap

Steel Trap

Caltrops

Increases Caltrops damage by 50%.
